    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Korean shamanic teaching: 'The drum is the shaman's horse — it carries the spirit between worlds'",
      "Pungmul proverb: 'The janggu speaks with two voices — the um and the yang cannot exist alone'",
      "Kim Duk-soo: 'Samulnori is not performance — it is argument, resolution, and transcendence in real time'"
    ],
    "revelation": "The Bone revealed: at 160 BPM with Log Drum×2 tuned apart (0 and +5 semitones), the high voice mimics the buk resonance and the low voice mimics the jing gong. The Frame Drum pair takes the janggu role — edge articulation on one creates the 'dung' stroke; open on the other creates the 'kung' stroke. circleAmount=0.2 preserves individual identity without full communion.",
    "god": "Bone",
    "flock_note": "The Pulse warned: at 160 BPM, humanize must stay low (0.2) or the jangdan pattern degrades into chaos. The precision IS the music — pungmul musicians train for years to achieve this.",
    "diagnosis": "Korean Pungmul is controlled ecstasy — 160 BPM of collective precision that reaches transcendence through discipline, not abandon."
  },
